      "id": "PopularPost36389",
      "post_content": "This card has quite a bit of Pros/Cons. Comparing this to cards like [Crusade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crusade) and [Bad Moon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bad Moon);  \n  \nPros:  \n  \nAll of you're creatures despite color.  \n  \nCons:  \n  \n2 more mana then the others.  \nOnly +1/0.  \nDoesn't add unless attacking.  \n  \nYeah. . . . IMO this card should have just been 2 and all Red creatures get +1/+1.",
